Injector/Manterror/Double Punch:



Injector walked up beside Cyber Claw.  "Don't ask me how this got here.  Me 
and my comrades only crashed onto the planet a short while ago, we don't know 
the history.  If you'd like to see Hell Beast to ask him where Megatron is, 
follow me." he said, walking off towards the bridge.

Manterror headed for the CR chamber.


Double Punch headed for his quarters, able to feel the Predacon base shake, 
he headed for the outside.
